info.title: Referential
info.description: The fastest API to access countries, states, cities, continents, dial and zip codes in up to 20 languages. A collection of data APIs to support forms, signups, search and lookup. Our endpoints are optimized for speed and size. Our data is regularly maintained and comes from International Standardization bodies, the United Nations, government surveys and GIS datasets. We do not scrape WikiPedia etc
info.x-long-description: The simplicity and speed of the API makes Referential ideal for direct invocation from forms, UX components, mobile apps and other mission critical applications where responsiveness and latency matter.
